document.full_text: forces loyal to libyan leader muammar gaddafi pressed further east with an artillery offensive against rebels on wednesday, and rebel fighters said western warplanes launched air strikes near ras lanuf, site of a major oil terminal.
document.title: gaddafi offensive pushes rebels back further east
